meaning_str.bing:
adv. （常用于否定句和疑问句句末）再也（不）
网络. 不再；再也不；还

（常用于否定句和疑问句句末）再也（不）

（常用于否定句和疑问句末）再也；再也不；再；不再；还

1.en: I would like to give assurance that our plans will not be subverted by the dark for they do not hold the cards any more.
1.cn: 我想在此作出保证我们的计划将不会被黑暗势力所破坏，因为他们已经没有任何牌可打。

2.en: Call it a coming attraction, because to know any more, you'll have to wait until Shane Salerno is good and ready to tell you.
2.cn: 之所以称之为潜在的诱惑，因为想知道得更多，你将不得不等到ShaneSalerno大发善心、愿意告诉你之时。

3.en: "Did you hear any more from the brewery? " she asked at the end of the week, hoping by the question to stir him on to action.
3.cn: “你有那家酿酒厂的消息了吗？”她在周末的时候问道，希望这样问能激其他的行动。

0.en: I don't wanna make any more rules.

1.en: Oh. Well. I'm not in his life. Not any more.
1.cn: 喔，不过，他的人生已经不要我了，再也不要我了。

2.en: Shouldn't have said that. No more questions! Don't ask any more questions. That's top secret like this.
2.cn: 不能说，别再问了，别再问任何问题，这是最高机密。

3.en: Come on. I don't want you thinking of me like that any more.

4.en: More importantly, you and your family, don't go to any more funerals.
4.cn: 更重要的是你跟你的家人不用再参加任何葬礼了。

5.en: Well, you don't have to do me any more favors, then. We're not going to hold each other back anymore, okay?
5.cn: 呃，那你不用再可怜我了，我们不要再彼此拖累了，好吧?

6.en: Happy Mrs. Chicken won't lay any more eggs. I am broken. Turn the computer off. Now turn it back on again.
6.cn: 能不能让快乐小鸡不要再下蛋了。出现故障。先把电脑关掉。然后再把它打开。

7.en: Happy Mrs. Chicken won't lay any more eggs. I am broken. Turn the computer off. Now turn it back on again.
7.cn: 能不能让快乐小鸡不要再下蛋了。出现故障。先把电脑关掉。然后再把它打开。

8.en: Look at me. I'm Chandler. Could I be wearing any more clothes?
8.cn: 你看看我，我是钱德！我还能再多穿一件衣服吗？

9.en: Just ask my dog. My vet says if I give her any more foie gras, she's going to die of gout.
9.cn: 不信问问我的狗，兽医说如果我再喂她鹅肝酱她就要死于痛风了。

10.en: No. I can't take any more secrets. I've got your secrets. I've got their secrets. I got secrets of my own, you know.
10.cn: 不要，我没办法再保密了，我有你们的秘密，他们的秘密，还有我自己的秘密。

11.en: I understand that if any more words come pouring out of your cunt mouth, I'm gonna have to eat every fucking chicken in this room.
11.cn: 我很清楚如果你这张臭嘴再蹦几个字出来，我就要吃光这房子里所有的鸡了。

12.en: Thousands of passengers' lives are on the line. All right, let's go out west to southern California tracon. Can you give us any more information?
12.cn: 几千乘客的生命都掌握在电话中。好的，从西转到南部，加利福尼亚管制中心。再给我们一点信息。

13.en: My dad, he heard I was gonna see you today, and he was all like, "Eddie, you tell that koala, I'm not funding any more of those shows, and that's final." Those were his words.
13.cn: 我老爸一听是你，就跟我急，“埃迪，告诉那只考拉，休想让我再赞助他”，这是他原话，骗你是小狗。

14.en: Ten years later when we all used to thinking about the coffee in a completely new domain, in a completely new approach, in a completely new price range, they don't need to pretend to be different any more.
14.cn: 十年之后，当我们都偏向于以这种新视角新工艺新价格去看待咖啡时，星巴克也就不需要再假装与众不同了。

15.en: Howard, can I see you for a minute, please? I don't want to show any more of your friends how I can fit in the booster seats. No, that's not it. Just come with me, please.
15.cn: 霍华德，我能找你有点事儿吗？我不想再给你的朋友们表演我是如何坐进幼儿加高座椅里了。额，不是让你做这个，请跟我来吧。

16.en: Shere Khan! Shere Khan! I'm not afraid of you! No one has to be afraid of you any more!
16.cn: 谢利·可汗！我现在不怕你了，从今以后再也不会有谁怕你了。

17.en: You don't keep it over here on this table any more? No, Eddie likes to keep it over there.
17.cn: 你不再把信放在这张桌上了？不了，艾迪喜欢把信放在那边。

18.en: George isn't afraid of heights any more. Oh, it is a bit high, isn't it? I'll just go down the stairs.
18.cn: 乔治再也不怕高了。噢，这有点高啊，对不对？我还是走楼梯吧。

19.en: But you see, the Chinese, they love their cars. I want to be fair, you do not see that many cyclists any more.
19.cn: 你可以看到，中国人非常喜欢他们的汽车，坦白的说，你再也看不到大量的自行车了。
